# ================================================================
# ML-BASED STOCK SELECTION SYSTEM FOR SHORT-TERM TRADING
# ================================================================
# Strategy  : Long top-N / Short bottom-N stocks, weekly rebalance
# Model     : LightGBM regressor (cross-sectional rank target)
# Hold      : 5 trading days
# Universe  : S&P 500 (configurable, default 100 stocks)
# Validated : Walk-forward expanding-window cross-validation
# Optimised : float32 throughout, chunked downloads, parquet cache
# Compatible: Google Colab · Python 3.9+ · yfinance 1.x
# ================================================================

